Persiapan Python 3.10 di Ubuntu

    Install Python 3.10

    bash
    sudo add-apt-repository ppa:deadsnakes/ppa
    sudo apt update
    sudo apt install python3.10 python3.10-venv python3.10-dev

Membuat Virtual Environment Project

    Buat dan aktifkan virtual environment di root folder project

    bash
    python3.10 -m venv .venv
    source .venv/bin/activate

Install Dependencies

    Isi dan install requirements.txt

    Contoh isi requirements.txt minimal:

text
numpy
pandas
matplotlib
seaborn
scipy
scikit-learn
tqdm
notebook
ipykernel
jupyterlab

Install semua paket:

    bash
    pip install --upgrade pip
    pip install -r requirements.txt

Registrasi Kernel Jupyter

    Daftarkan kernel agar muncul di pilihan notebook

    bash
    python -m ipykernel install --user --name=venv-py310 --display-name="Python (venv-py310)"

Menjalankan Notebook

    Jalankan Jupyter Notebook atau Jupyter Lab

bash
jupyter notebook

atau

bash
jupyter lab

Pilih kernel "Python (venv-py310)" saat mulai notebook.